    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Correspondence
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Letters from the Culture Secretary to the BBC and S4C on the 2022 Licence Fee Settlement
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">On 10 November, the Culture Secretary, Oliver Dowden, wrote to the BBC and S4C to formally begin the process to agree the level of the licence fee from 2022.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
